    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong data-start=\"528\" data-end=\"550\">Relentless Pursuit</strong></p><h3 data-start=\"552\" data-end=\"584\"><strong data-start=\"556\" data-end=\"571\">Description</strong> (copy/paste)</h3><p data-start=\"585\" data-end=\"664\"><strong data-start=\"585\" data-end=\"623\">Relentless Pursuit (Passive; Rage)</strong><br data-start=\"623\" data-end=\"626\" />No prey escapes once the chase begins.</p><p data-start=\"666\" data-end=\"800\">While <strong data-start=\"672\" data-end=\"682\">raging</strong>, when you <strong data-start=\"693\" data-end=\"711\">hit a creature</strong>, you may reduce that creature’s <strong data-start=\"744\" data-end=\"764\">speed by 10 feet</strong> until the <strong data-start=\"775\" data-end=\"799\">end of its next turn</strong>.</p><p data-start=\"802\" data-end=\"905\">If the creature is already <strong data-start=\"829\" data-end=\"863\">restrained, grappled, or prone</strong>, this reduction increases to <strong data-start=\"893\" data-end=\"904\">20 feet</strong>.</p><p data-start=\"907\" data-end=\"951\">You can apply this effect <strong data-start=\"933\" data-end=\"950\">once per turn</strong>.</p><hr data-start=\"953\" data-end=\"956\" /><p data-start=\"958\" data-end=\"1018\"><code data-start=\"979\" data-end=\"1018\">[GAROU_FEATURE] id=relentless-pursuit</code></p>",
